1. *Promenio* sam planove za vikend. (I changed my plans for the weekend.)
2. Da li bi mogao da mi *promeniš* ovaj novčanik? (Could you change this wallet for me?)
3. On je već *promenio* tri posla ove godine. (He has already changed three jobs this year.)
4. Moramo *promeniti* strategiju ako želimo da ostvarimo cilj. (We need to change our strategy if we want to achieve our goal.)
5. Nisam siguran da li bih *promenio* svoju odluku da sam znao ovo pre. (I'm not sure if I would have changed my decision if I knew this earlier.)
6. *Promenila* sam frizuru, kako ti se sviđa? (I changed my hairstyle, how do you like it?)
7. Da li bi *promenio* nešto u svojoj prošlosti da možeš? (Would you change anything in your past if you could?)
8. Kako da *promenimo* tu naviku koja nam šteti? (How can we change that habit that's harmful to us?)
9. Ovaj proizvod ne mogu da *promenim* jer sam ga otvorio. (I can't exchange this product because I opened it.)
10. Ako želimo da napredujemo, moramo se *promeniti* i prilagoditi novim okolnostima. (If we want to make progress, we must change and adapt to new circumstances.)